#### Token Dispenser for a Pharmacy
    Token contains:
        • Serial Number
        • Date and Timestamp


    User Types:
        • Customer who gets a token
        • 3 Agents who process tokens of a customer

    Requirements:
        # Front-End:
            • UI (using PySimpleGUI)
        
        # Back-End:
            • fastAPI to build API functionality
            • Storage (can be DBMS or simple file system).


    Reporting Statistics (metrics):
        • Expected waiting time.
        • How many persons are still in the queue.
        • What is the total time needed to clean up the queue. To know when to stop taking more customers in order to close the business.
